1988-04-10  Vern Paxson <vern@ee.lbl.gov>

	* NEWS, README: Initial revision

1988-04-10  Vern Paxson <vern@ee.lbl.gov>

	* yylex.c: added identifying comment.  changed to include "parse.h"
	instead of "y.tab.h"

